Reports and Financials Module Description
The Reports and Financials module provides comprehensive insights into the business's performance by generating accurate reports on sales, inventory, purchases, and financial transactions. It helps managers and business owners monitor operations, evaluate profitability, and make informed decisions.
Key Functions:
Generate daily, weekly, monthly, and annual sales reports.
View inventory reports, including stock levels, stock movements, and low-stock items.
Create purchase reports to track supplier orders and expenses.
Monitor revenue, expenses, and overall business profitability.
Generate profit and loss summaries.
View payment and transaction history.
Export reports in PDF or Excel format for record-keeping and analysis.
Display charts and graphs for sales trends, inventory performance, and financial summaries.
Filter reports by date, product, supplier, branch, or employee.
Benefits:
Provides real-time insights into business performance.
Supports better financial planning and decision-making.
Improves inventory and sales monitoring.
Simplifies financial record management.
Helps identify sales trends, profitable products, and business growth opportunities.
